==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Reword
<hw>Re*word"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
repeat in the same words; to reecho.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To alter the wording of; to restate in other words;
<as>as, to <ex>reword</ex> an idea or a passage</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rewrite</ent>⟦br⟧
